Text.SourceString: Ah, goomgoom!
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, goomgoom!

Text.SourceString: A hooman can see <NPCName>Groo</>.
Text.LocalizedString: A hooman can see <NPCName>Groo</>.

Text.SourceString: Wheeee! <NPCName>Groo</> can run again.
Text.LocalizedString: Wheeee! <NPCName>Groo</> can run again.

Text.SourceString: Hooman! Go run too! Wheeeee!
Text.LocalizedString: Hooman! Go run too! Wheeeee!

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Groo</> don't remember how to things after stuck for so long.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Groo</> don't remember how to things after stuck for so long.

Text.SourceString: Aaah... Wind.
Text.LocalizedString: Aaah... Wind.

Text.SourceString: Giants can help you.//Giants grow food too.
Text.LocalizedString: Giants can help you.//Giants grow food too.

Text.SourceString: Giants the best food grower. Hooman lose.//Heh heh heh!
Text.LocalizedString: Giants the best food grower. Hooman lose.//Heh heh heh!

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Groo</> collects food from forest.//Hooman too, goom?
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Groo</> collects food from forest.//Hooman too, goom?

Text.SourceString: Goddess food the best!//Better than Giant's.
Text.LocalizedString: Goddess food the best!//Better than Giant's.

Text.SourceString: Hooman done talking to <NPCName>Groo</>? I want to run and pick fruit!
Text.LocalizedString: Hooman done talking to <NPCName>Groo</>? I want to run and pick fruit!

Text.SourceString: I don't sleep.//<NPCName>Groo</> strong.
Text.LocalizedString: I don't sleep.//<NPCName>Groo</> strong.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Groo</> fix tool.//The best. Heh heh heh!
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Groo</> fix tool.//The best. Heh heh heh!

Text.SourceString: Hooman, thank for saving <NPCName>Groo</>. Now <NPCName>Groo</> is not stone anymore!
Text.LocalizedString: Hooman, thank for saving <NPCName>Groo</>. Now <NPCName>Groo</> is not stone anymore!

Text.SourceString: Giants like town. Many yummy food.
Text.LocalizedString: Giants like town. Many yummy food.

Text.SourceString: Giants hate town. Many bouncy hooman.
Text.LocalizedString: Giants hate town. Many bouncy hooman.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Grog</> is too slow! But <NPCName>Grog</> is friend, even when sooooo slooooow.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Grog</> is too slow! But <NPCName>Grog</> is friend, even when sooooo slooooow.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Groo</> ask <NPCName>Gong</> to run but <NPCName>Gong</> says too tired.//<NPCName>Gong</> old. Heh heh heh!
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Groo</> ask <NPCName>Gong</> to run but <NPCName>Gong</> says too tired.//<NPCName>Gong</> old. Heh heh heh!

Text.SourceString: Hooman want better tool? <NPCName>Groo</> can help!//But only two. Not allowed more.
Text.LocalizedString: Hooman want better tool? <NPCName>Groo</> can help!//But only two. Not allowed more.

Text.SourceString: Why Hooman stop <NPCName>Groo</>? <NPCName>Groo</> busy!
Text.LocalizedString: Why Hooman stop <NPCName>Groo</>? <NPCName>Groo</> busy!

Text.SourceString: Giants work better together.//If Hooman want better tool, save more Giants.
Text.LocalizedString: Giants work better together.//If Hooman want better tool, save more Giants.

Text.SourceString: Ah, goom, Hooman. Yes.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, goom, Hooman. Yes.

Text.SourceString: Everything so wet!//Last time <NPCName>Groo</> fall and hit head...
Text.LocalizedString: Everything so wet!//Last time <NPCName>Groo</> fall and hit head...

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>GONG</> SKY LEAK TOO MUCH AGAIN! ARGH!
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>GONG</> SKY LEAK TOO MUCH AGAIN! ARGH!

Text.SourceString: Giants need fire... Cold outside.//Hm, now <NPCName>Groo</> sad...
Text.LocalizedString: Giants need fire... Cold outside.//Hm, now <NPCName>Groo</> sad...

Text.SourceString: Don't remember anything from stone age...//<NPCName>Groo</> got stoned and slept.
Text.LocalizedString: Don't remember anything from stone age...//<NPCName>Groo</> got stoned and slept.

Text.SourceString: Hooman go to cavern, yes? Where <NPCName>Groo</> was stone?//Why?! It scary!
Text.LocalizedString: Hooman go to cavern, yes? Where <NPCName>Groo</> was stone?//Why?! It scary!

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Groo</> likes to run through the leaves. Wheeeee!//Wind the best! Better than water. Heh heh heh!
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Groo</> likes to run through the leaves. Wheeeee!//Wind the best! Better than water. Heh heh heh!

Text.SourceString: Snowpeople look like Giants sometimes.//Only the good ones.
Text.LocalizedString: Snowpeople look like Giants sometimes.//Only the good ones.

Text.SourceString: Bored! <NPCName>Groo</> just want to run in the forest.//Doing useless stuff like Hooman. I want.
Text.LocalizedString: Bored! <NPCName>Groo</> just want to run in the forest.//Doing useless stuff like Hooman. I want.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Gong</> is fast sometimes! Like the wind.//But only sometimes. Most times, <NPCName>Groo</> is faster. Like the wind. Woosh!
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Gong</> is fast sometimes! Like the wind.//But only sometimes. Most times, <NPCName>Groo</> is faster. Like the wind. Woosh!

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Groo</> is feeling slow today...//It must be what Hooman feel all time.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Groo</> is feeling slow today...//It must be what Hooman feel all time.

Text.SourceString: Storm so fast! Maybe one day <NPCName>Groo</> can be as fast as storm.
Text.LocalizedString: Storm so fast! Maybe one day <NPCName>Groo</> can be as fast as storm.

Text.SourceString: Why can Hooman see Giants? Other hooman in hooman village can't.//Strange it is...
Text.LocalizedString: Why can Hooman see Giants? Other hooman in hooman village can't.//Strange it is...

Text.SourceString: Why Hooman look like that? So tall. Eyes so big and strange...
Text.LocalizedString: Why Hooman look like that? So tall. Eyes so big and strange...

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Groo</> not like village when rain like this. Too slippy!
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Groo</> not like village when rain like this. Too slippy!

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Groo</> not like village when rain like this. Too slippy!
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Groo</> not like village when rain like this. Too slippy!

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Groo</> not like village when snow like this. Too slippy!
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Groo</> not like village when snow like this. Too slippy!

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Groo</> tired today. Maybe go outside later.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Groo</> tired today. Maybe go outside later.

Text.SourceString: Sun is like eye, yes? Watching us all during the day.
Text.LocalizedString: Sun is like eye, yes? Watching us all during the day.

Text.SourceString: So loud outside!
Text.LocalizedString: So loud outside!

Text.SourceString: White fluffy cold, white fluffy cold~
Text.LocalizedString: White fluffy cold, white fluffy cold~

Text.SourceString: So much nice nice fruit now! Forest is rich. Sprouting Season here!//Giants grow seeds in forest too for animal friends.
Text.LocalizedString: So much nice nice fruit now! Forest is rich. Sprouting Season here!//Giants grow seeds in forest too for animal friends.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes <NPCName>Groo</> see small hooman eating lot of colorful things on stick. Look so nice and yum yum!//Small hooman can see Giants. Yes.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes <NPCName>Groo</> see small hooman eating lot of colorful things on stick. Look so nice and yum yum!//Small hooman can see Giants. Yes.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Groo</> a little sad leaves are falling but <NPCName>Groo</> know leaves will be back in Sprouting Season.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Groo</> a little sad leaves are falling but <NPCName>Groo</> know leaves will be back in Sprouting Season.

Text.SourceString: Time to see pretty flowers. Busy time for Giants.
Text.LocalizedString: Time to see pretty flowers. Busy time for Giants.

Text.SourceString: Hooman always get together near lake in Sprouting Season.//Food smells yummy! Giants want to join.
Text.LocalizedString: Hooman always get together near lake in Sprouting Season.//Food smells yummy! Giants want to join.

Text.SourceString: Forest so full again! Giants home.//Thank you, Hooman.
Text.LocalizedString: Forest so full again! Giants home.//Thank you, Hooman.

Text.SourceString: So many new sprouts this Sprouting Season. Nice to see.//It make wind smell yummy.
Text.LocalizedString: So many new sprouts this Sprouting Season. Nice to see.//It make wind smell yummy.

Text.SourceString: Maybe <NPCName>Groo</> not zoom so much now. Slippy ice.
Text.LocalizedString: Maybe <NPCName>Groo</> not zoom so much now. Slippy ice.
